{"type":"message","id":"28206b5c","parentId":"7c724e48","timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:40:00.819Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full picture of the DTLX project. Let me compile the status report.\n\n**DTLX Backend (Project ID: 77055841):**\n- Local: branch `feature/clean-architecture-migration`, commit `47d53ae` (Mar 30)\n- Active branches: `develop`, `feature/clean-architecture-migration`, `refactor/main`, `production`, `main`, etc.\n- **MR !166**: `feature/clean-architecture-migration` → `refactor/main` — status `can_be_merged`, no conflicts\n- **Other unmerged branches**:\n  - `fix/build-operability-and-typos` \n  - `fix/conflict-production-v1.1.0` (already merged)\n  - `hotfix/import-student`\n  - `hotfix/unicode-normalization-nfc`\n  - `optimization/conventions`\n  - `refactor/antigravity`\n  - `refactor/merge-api-common`\n  - `refactor/split-app-server`\n- **Merged**: `feature/api-refactor`, `feature/docs-api`, `fix/add-student-to-course`, `hotfix/docker`, `refactor/code-cleanup-phase-2`\n\n**DTLX Frontend (Project ID: 77055851):**\n- No local clone\n- No opened MRs\n- Last activity: Apr 7\n\nThe main priority is merging MR !166 for the backend refactor, while the frontend needs to be set up locally and doesn't have any active merge requests.","thinkingSignature":"2b8b72db8265447792a00a9523c48d3f7cca1c9176a76869bc1f8d7d2dfaa9b8"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 DTLX — Project Track\n\n---\n\n### 🖥️ DTLX Backend (`ahv-dtlx-backend`) — Project ID: 77055841\n\n| Trạng thái | Chi tiết |\n|---|---|\n| **Local branch** | `feature/clean-architecture-migration` |\n| **Last commit** | `47d53ae` — chore: course student repository! (Mar 30) |\n| **Local sync** | ⚠️ Local behind `develop` by ~1 month |\n\n**MRs mở:**\n\n| MR | Source → Target | Trạng thái | Link |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **!166** 🟡 | `feature/clean-architecture-migration` → `refactor/main` | ✅ Can merge, no conflicts | [🔗](https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/merge_requests/166) |\n\n**Branches chưa merge (unmerged):**\n- `fix/build-operability-and-typos`\n- `hotfix/import-student`\n- `hotfix/unicode-normalization-nfc` — NFC unicode normalization fix\n- `optimization/conventions`\n- `refactor/antigravity`\n- `refactor/merge-api-common`\n- `refactor/split-app-server`\n\n---\n\n### 🖥️ DTLX Frontend (`ahv-dtlx-frontend`) — Project ID: 77055851\n\n| Trạng thái | Chi tiết |\n|---|---|\n| **Local** | ❌ Chưa clone |\n| **MRs mở** | Không có |\n| **Last activity** | Apr 7, 2026 (stale ~6 days) |\n\n---\n\n### 📋 Action Items\n\n| # | Task | Ưu tiên |\n|---|---|---|\n| 1 | Merge MR **!166** (clean-architecture → refactor/main) | 🔴 Cao |\n| 2 | Clone & setup DTLX FE local | 🔴 Cao |\n| 3 | Sync BE `develop` vs local `feature/clean-architecture-migration` | 🟡 Trung |\n| 4 | Review unmerged branches | 🟡 Trung |\n\nLead muốn Orbis xử lý bước nào?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":8213,"output":816,"cacheRead":62486,"cacheWrite":3333,"totalTokens":74848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776055181338,"responseId":"062ba68f0d223c65002d2a273a3647f7"}}
