{"type":"compaction","id":"5d10587a","parentId":"1aa7107d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T03:07:02.478Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. **QLHV**: Complete BE/FE branch merge to `develop` — BE MR !6 already created and awaiting Lead approval/merge; FE already merged by Lead.\n2. **DTLX Backend**: Fix 35+ TypeScript build errors in `feature/clean-architecture-migration` branch, then start the server on port 5555.\n3. **DTLX Frontend**: Already running on port 3000 (started manually).\n4. **System deployment**: Deploy full DTLX system (FE + BE working together).\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Orbis is ONLY allowed to work on ahv-qlhv project (confirmed by Lead Apr 12 13:57).\n- For DTLX work (API testing/deployment), Lead later asked for full system deployment (Apr 14 01:44, \"triển khai toàn bộ hệ thống\" / \"làm từng module một\").\n- API testing should be done module-by-module after backend is fixed.\n- Never push or commit code; read-only API testing only.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] QLHV BE `feat/notification-migration` pushed to GitLab\n- [x] QLHV BE MR !6 created: `feat/notification-migration` → `develop` (ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be!6)\n- [x] QLHV FE `feat/database-master` merged into `develop` (done by Lead manually, commit `3259abe`)\n- [x] DTLX FE started: http://localhost:3000 (Vite, port 3000, VITE_API_SERVER=http://localhost:5555, branch `main`)\n- [x] QLHV BE and FE servers started (BE on port 5002, FE on port 3000 — Apr 12 session; later restarted)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **DTLX BE build fix** — 35+ TypeScript errors blocking `yarn build` and server start on port 5555\n\n### Blocked\n- DTLX Backend cannot start until TypeScript errors are fixed\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **FE and BE run independently**: DTLX FE (port 3000) is running; BE (port 5555) is blocked by build errors.\n- **DTLX BE testing deferred**: Module-by-module API testing (auth → system → education → operation → notification) will begin only after BE is running.\n- **Senior agents spawned**: `senior-backend` and `senior-frontend` agents were spawned for DTLX deployment but all timed out; manual deployment proceeded instead.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. **Fix DTLX BE TypeScript errors** in `feature/clean-architecture-migration` branch (`/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend`):\n   - Core issue: interface mismatch — services return `data` but interfaces expect `docs`; pagination uses `limit` vs `itemsPerPage`\n   - Key files with errors:\n     - `src/modules/coursesStudents/coursesStudents.controller.ts` — `.data` not in response type\n     - `src/modules/coursesStudents/coursesStudents.service.ts` — return type mismatch\n     - `src/migration/migration.ts` — `.data` missing from filter response types\n     - `src/modules/devices/...service.ts`, `examRegistrations`, `examResults`, `examSchedules` — `IMeta` missing `currentPage`, `itemsPerPage`\n     - `src/modules/lessons.service.ts` — returns `docs` instead of `data`\n     - `src/middlewares/helpers/permission.helper.ts` — missing `permissions.json` and `routeDetailForPermissions.json`\n     - `src/application/usecases/teachers/GetTeacherRankingsUseCase.ts` — missing `result` property\n     - `src/modules/workCalendars/workCalendars.controller.ts` — `.data` not in response type\n2. After build succeeds: start BE on port 5555\n3. Test APIs module-by-module: auth (public) → system → education → operation → notification (protected)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **QLHV BE MR !6**: https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/merge_requests/6 — needs Lead approval/merge\n- **QLHV BE workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be`\n- **DTLX BE workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend`, branch `feature/clean-architecture-migration`, commit `47d53ae1`\n- **DTLX FE workspace**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-frontend`, branch `main`, running on port 3000\n- **DTLX BE project ID**: 77055841, **FE project ID**: 77055851\n- **DTLX BE env**: `.env` (copied from `.env.example`), PORT=5555, MongoDB `mongodb://localhost:27017/dtlx` (running), Redis `localhost:6379/9` (running)\n- **DTLX BE build command**: `yarn build` (fails) → `yarn dev` (nodemon `src/server.ts`)\n- **DTLX FE build**: already built and running (node_modules present, vite binary exists)\n- **Backend processes currently running**: DTLX FE (`clear-mist`, port 3000)\n- **Backend processes killed**: DTLX BE attempts (`oceanic-cove`, `sharp-ember`) — SIGKILL (memory/resource limits)\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"2535997b","tokensBefore":130417,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/skills/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json"]},"fromHook":false}
